          "settings": {
            "heading": "Details",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<h6><strong>HOW IT FEELS.</strong></h6><h6>Exceptionally plush with a smooth, velvety hand-feel. </h6><h6><strong>WHY IT'S BETTER.</strong></h6><h6>Our towels dry quickly, resist pilling, maintain color richness, and are crafted to stay luxuriously soft for years — not months. </h6><h6><strong>OUR MATERIALS.</strong></h6><h6>Crafted from 700 GSM, 100% Long-Staple Turkish Cotton for unmatched softness, exceptional absorbency, and lasting strength. Certified by OEKO-TEX® to ensure your towels are safe for you, your skin, and the environment.</h6><ul><li><h6>100% Long-Staple Cotton</h6></li><li><h6>Premium 700 GSM Weight</h6></li><li><h6>Silky, spa-grade softness</h6></li><li><h6>Fast-drying & ultra-absorbent</h6></li><li><h6>Colorfast & fade-resistant</h6></li><li><h6>OEKO-TEX® Certified</h6></li><li><h6>Woven dobby border</h6></li><li><h6>Double-stitched edges for durability</h6></li></ul>",
