        "collapsible-row-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "FAQ",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p><strong>Q: Will these towels stay soft after washing?</strong><br/><strong>A:</strong> Yes — and many say they get even softer. Just wash warm, tumble dry low, and skip fabric softener (it coats the fibers).</p><p>‎</p><p><strong>Q: Are they good for sensitive skin?</strong><br/><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely. Our towels are made from hypoallergenic, OEKO-TEX® certified Turkish cotton — gentle, pure, and skin-safe.</p><p>‎</p><p><strong>Q: Do they dry quickly?</strong><br/><strong>A:</strong> Yes. Despite their plush feel, the breathable cotton and zero-twist weave help them dry fast between uses.</p><p>‎</p><p><strong>Q: What if I don’t love them?</strong><br/><strong>A:</strong> No worries — try them for 30 days, risk-free. If you’re not happy, we’ll refund you. No hassle, no questions.</p><p></p><p><a href=\"/pages/faq-1\" title=\"FAQ\">More Questions?</a></p>",
